_sText: This is just a crazy idea that I had, and finally I am releasing the map ^^ It includes a lot of textures, which are custom and made by me, except for the skybox though, but everything else is made by me, It's a simple map and I hope it's fun :D I made a radar for it, but the file size was too big, so instead of it being 12.2 MB I removed the radar and now it's 6.88 MB which is better when people download it. If you really want the radar version you can ask me cause I have it on my computer ;) The map includes: - Custom textures - Custom skybox - 64 +, total spawn points - rainbows ^^ and of course I made a video for this as well ^^ Check it out here, and it's in HD ^^ and subscribe to my youtube account if you will ^^ Enjoy and have fun!
